ID: TC_005

Title: Verify All Products list

Priority: High

Severity: Major

Preconditions:
* At least 1 product exists in system
* Products page accessible without login

Steps:
1. Navigate to “https://automationexercise.com/products”
2. Wait for products list to load


Expected result:
1. Products page loads successfully:
- URL: https://automationexercise.com/products
- "ALL PRODUCTS" heading visible

2. Products list displayed:
- Minimum 1 product visible
- Products shown in grid/list layout

3. Each product card contains:
- Product image (no broken)
- Product name (visible and readable)
- Price (format: Rs. XXX or similar)
- "View Product" button (visible and clickable)

4. Page loads without errors

5. No broken images or missing data

Actual result

Status: Not Run